{"tid":558504,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"原來曼城贏多6場，就會係摩佬面前奪冠。","createTime":"2018-02-12T10:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T11:27:12.000Z","uid":19889,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a1118dcf263b3150e6ffeff546ac16e79a1e88f1","tid":558504,"uid":19889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:34:38.000Z","msg":"隨曼聯失分，曼城目前已經於英超聯賽榜領先次席對手16分之多，奪冠幾乎已成事實，餘下問題在於他們何時封王。照目前走勢，曼城甚或有機會打破最快封王紀錄，而當中最有可能成為「攔路虎」的正是同市死敵曼聯。<br />\n<br />\n曼城目前餘下11場聯賽，在領先16分下只要餘下6場全勝即可肯定提早封王。而最巧合的是，「藍月亮」在聯賽未來第6戰的對手正正是同市死敵曼聯。換句話說，曼城何時封王除了取決於曼聯作為聯賽「二哥」的成績外，想靠自己亦要先過「紅魔鬼」一關。不過先不論曼聯表現如何，曼城未來賽程亦不易打，當中主要對手包括阿仙奴、車路士及愛華頓等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b159ab4c4c37d7838a108986ebf4f5b07570d87a","tid":558504,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:35:50.000Z","msg":"過到車犬阿犬先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4af3f65738ed8e968c0edecfc2d22590992179","tid":558504,"uid":135410,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"b159ab4c4c37d7838a108986ebf4f5b07570d87a","tid":558504,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:35:50.000Z","msg":"過到車犬阿犬先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:37:30.000Z","msg":"兩大垃圾點會過唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d19e627bde3339016e17bfb1644f9ee7ea8c27","tid":558504,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T10:38:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9e95ed78848bbcc938166d2ef64ad737c521376","tid":558504,"uid":5649,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9b4af3f65738ed8e968c0edecfc2d22590992179","tid":558504,"uid":135410,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"b159ab4c4c37d7838a108986ebf4f5b07570d87a","tid":558504,"uid":5649,"like":0